humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the report, metastatic adenocarcinoma is identified in 3 out of 27 right axillary lymph nodes. Based on the new rules provided, N1 indicates metastases in 1 to 3 axillary lymph nodes. Therefore, the N stage for this patient's cancer is N1.
